1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with 3D human pose estimation using depth prediction network. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a neural network for predicting joints in a camera centered coordinate system. 
3. cs.RO (Robotics) is another possible category as the paper deals with human pose estimation which is relevant to robotics applications. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a novel approach for human pose estimation using a neural network. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with 3D human pose estimation which is relevant to computer graphics applications.
